# Account info
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User mikolaj.gawrys@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.google-app-pass"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt


# Remote storage
IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail


# Local storage
MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/gmail/ 
Inbox ~/mail/gmail/Inbox


Channel gmail
Near :gmail-local:
Far :gmail-remote:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Bin"
Create Both
SyncState *